data.description: This beautiful two-story home features a study with double doors. You'll also find upgraded Shaw® carpeting at the bedrooms and den, with Shaw® vinyl plank flooring at the study, and Emser® tile flooring at the entry, living area, kitchen, dining room, and baths. The kitchen offers granite countertops with glossy Daltile® Elevare(tm) tile backsplash, a Moen® Camerist high arc faucet, and a Whirlpool® ceramic glass cooktop, single wall oven, microwave/hood combination, and 4-cycle dishwasher. The master bath boasts a 42-in. separate marble garden tub and shower with tile surround, and an extended cabinet with knee space. Additional features include a wireless security system, upgraded Sherwin-Williams® interior paint, a covered patio, and full yard sprinkler system.
